This paper discusses the intersection of data science and social justice, which falls under the category of computational social science (cs.CY) and computer science and society (cs.CS). The paper also touches on issues related to data security and privacy (cs.CR) and the use of data in public health (cs.PH) and information systems (cs.SI).
